{"title":"井冈山泉","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":1,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常饮幸福水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更爱井冈山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山中泉水流不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大小五井永不干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流不断，永不干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涓涓细流汇大川；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"营地红旗漫卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银河倒挂白云间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席汲水磨墨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写下雄文一篇篇；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们蘸水磨刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥看星火可燎原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走遍天下路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征途春色添，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南北转战几十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总有山泉润心田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常饮井冈水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牢记井冈山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈泉，源头远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"源远流长水更甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千山万岭清泉涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千江万河浪花翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问发源地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在井冈山……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}